posts.title: Late Night Crew: Danger To Our Democracy Edition
posts.content:
Welcome to another edition of the Late Night Crew! Tonight, I'm your host u/danneskjold, and we have u/RuprechtThaMonkeyBoy on tunes again. He's doing a great job picking them out and I think tonight is no exception.

Tonight let's talk about - what does a "Danger to our Democracy" look like? The left has used this phrase to describe President Trump, as part of their efforts to work up their radicalized base to do something crazy like trying to assassinate him. But who is the real "Danger to our Democracy?" I say it's the left, who are ditching the concept for which their party is supposedly named.

Today as you all know, Joe Biden dropped out of the 2024 Presidential race and endorsed Kamala Harris as his replacement. Kamala has announced that she is running for President and rebranded the Biden for President organization as her own. She also has the support of the DNC delegates from Tennessee, who voted today unanimously to support her instead of Biden.

Tell me again how President Trump is the Danger to our Democracy.

Tonight I have a message for the Democrats who have always wanted to run for President but never could win an election. You hear that Beto? Stacy Abrams? Now's your chance! If you want to be the Democrat nominee, all you have to do is get in good with the DNC and they will select you! You don't have to win a single primary election. You don't have to hustle state-to-state meeting any of those pesky voters. Just promise to be the DNC's little puppet, because you know that's what they love. They've been used to controlling Joe Biden, and they would be happy for anyone to take over who won't prosecute them for their crimes.

You know, I grew up with Democrat friends. They stopped talking to me since I supported Trump, but they always accused the Republican Party of being out of touch. They claimed they were good ol' boys smoking cigars making backroom decisions that affect the people without caring what any of them think. Now this is exactly what the Democrat Party is doing. It's about the most anti-democratic thing they could do, yet here they are showing their true colors. Democrats are the true Danger to our Democracy.

So keep the salt mines running tonight while the left implodes on itself. I have no idea who President Trump will be running against in November, and neither do they. It's a beautiful thing, and it's all just going to lead to a Trump landslide. So pop some popcorn, enjoy the show, and enjoy some tunes tonight!

  • Billy Squier - The Stroke
  • The Rentals - Friends of P.
  • Beastie Boys - Sabotage
  • The English Beat - Rotating Heads
  • Bryan Lewis - I Think My Dog's a Democrat
  • Rush - The Big Money
